Script 1 — Detect IAM Users Without MFA
Security best practice:
All IAM users must have MFA
Python script:
import boto3
iam = boto3.client('iam')
users = iam.list_users()
for user in users['Users']:
    mfa = iam.list_mfa_devices(UserName=user['UserName'])
    if len(mfa['MFADevices']) == 0:
        print("User without MFA:", user['UserName'])
Output example:
User without MFA: dev-user
User without MFA: test-user
________________________________________
Script 2 — Detect Inactive Users
Inactive users are security risks.
import boto3
from datetime import datetime, timedelta
iam = boto3.client('iam')
users = iam.list_users()
for user in users['Users']:
    if 'PasswordLastUsed' in user:
        last_used = user['PasswordLastUsed']
        if last_used < datetime.now(last_used.tzinfo) - timedelta(days=90):
            print("Inactive user:", user['UserName'])
