6. Step 2 — Automate User Creation (Python)
When HR adds a user, automation creates IAM accounts.
Example script:
import boto3

iam = boto3.client('iam')

def create_user(username):
    iam.create_user(UserName=username)

    iam.add_user_to_group(
        GroupName='Developers',
        UserName=username
    )

create_user("dev-user1")
Production logic:
department → IAM group
role → permissions
Example:
DevOps → DevOpsGroup
Developer → DevGroup
Security → SecurityGroup
