7. Step 3 — IAM Access Audit Automation
Daily script checks:
•	MFA enabled
•	inactive users
•	admin roles
•	policy violations
Example Python script:
import boto3

iam = boto3.client('iam')

users = iam.list_users()

for user in users['Users']:
    mfa = iam.list_mfa_devices(UserName=user['UserName'])

    if len(mfa['MFADevices']) == 0:
        print("MFA not enabled:", user['UserName'])
