9. Step 5 — Generate IAM Access Reports
Generate compliance reports automatically.
Example script:
import boto3
import csv

iam = boto3.client('iam')

users = iam.list_users()

with open("iam_report.csv","w") as f:
    writer = csv.writer(f)

    writer.writerow(["UserName","CreatedDate"])

    for user in users['Users']:
        writer.writerow([user['UserName'],user['CreateDate']])
Reports can be stored in S3.
